title: PDF to CBR converter
description: I am uploading a small utility for converting all your pdf files to CBR. The program converts all images in a PDF document to Jpg and archives them in .cbr extension for viewing in CDisplay. Plus you can also get your Jpg files loose if you dont want them to be archived. Its a small utility and very lite on your PC too. Thanks to Impala07 for helping me out with it. Enjoy and Seed.
